    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how smoothly it handles!",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
